# Local dev: rembg's model cache (170 MB ONNX) when running inside the
# Docker container with a bind-mount. The Dockerfile bakes it into
# /app/.u2net/ in the IMAGE; the host-side dir under the repo is just
# a side-effect of the bind-mount and shouldn't be committed.
.u2net/

# Local dev: pip user-install dir from `docker compose exec web pip
# install` rescues when a Dockerfile rebuild fails (see CLAUDE.md).
# Ephemeral — disappears on `docker compose down`; never committed.
.local/
